'''罗克斯基隧道'''（{{lang-ka|როკის გვირაბი}}；[[奥塞梯语|奥塞梯语]]: Ручъы тъунел；{{lang-ru|Рокский туннель}}）或'''羅基隧道'''（Roki tunnel）是一条属于[[外高加索公路|外高加索公路]]，穿越[[大高加索山脉|大高加索山脉]]的高山[[隧道|隧道]]，最北端是Upper Roka村。这是唯一一条连接[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[北奧塞提亞|北奧塞提亞]]和[[格鲁吉亚|格鲁吉亚]]分裂势力[[南奥塞梯|南奥塞梯]]的通道。隧道在北奧塞提亞[[Nizhny_Zaramag|Nizhny Zaramag]]开始载人，有时称为[[Roki|Roki]]-[[Nizhny_Zaramag|Nizhny Zaramag]]过境线。

隧道在1984年由[[苏联|苏联]]建成，并是少数几个穿越北高加索的线路之一。隧道大约海拔2000米，长3730米，在靠近Roki山口时，海拔3000米，并只能在夏季使用<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://derstandard.at/?url=%2F%3Fid%3D1218534230819 |title=Der Roki-Tunnel - Schlüsselstelle im Georgien-Konflikt |access-date=2022-03-25 |archive-date=2009-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090723002133/http://derstandard.at/?url=%2F%3Fid%3D1218534230819 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Structurae.de: Roki Tunnel | publisher = Structurae.de | url = http://en.structurae.de/structures/data/index.cfm?id=s0021059 | accessdate = 2008-08-10 | archive-date = 2015-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151226012425/http://structurae.net/structures/roki-tunnel | dead-url = no }}</ref> 其他穿越北高加索的线路包括在2006年6月关闭的穿越格鲁吉亚和俄罗斯的[[卡兹别吉|卡兹别吉]]-[[Verkhni_Lars|Verkhni Lars]]海关检查站的[[格鲁吉亚军用通道|格鲁吉亚军用通道]]，<ref>http://groups.msn.com/justicefornorthcaucasus/osetia.msnw?action=get_message&mview=0&ID_Message=12992 {{Wayback|url=http://groups.msn.com/justicefornorthcaucasus/osetia.msnw?action=get_message&mview=0&ID_Message=12992 |date=20080908063201 }} (accessed 2008-8-10)</ref>和格鲁吉亚认为非法运作的位于[[阿布哈兹|阿布哈兹]]的穿越[[Gantiadi|Gantiadi]]-[[Adler|Adler]]的路线。 <ref>http://www.kommersant.com/page.asp?idr=527&id=688852 {{Wayback|url=http://www.kommersant.com/page.asp?idr=527&id=688852 |date=20060715163021 }} (accessed 2008-8-10)</ref>

这条隧道在整个[[格鲁吉亚和奧塞提亞冲突|格鲁吉亚和奧塞提亞冲突]]中起到重要作用。南奥塞梯当局把这条隧道的过境费当做他们的主要收入来源。[[美国|美国]]支持下的格鲁吉亚政府呼吁在南奥塞梯一端的隧道交由国际监督员控制，而不是南奥塞梯分裂势力与俄罗斯维和部队。<ref>{{cite web | title = Georgian rebel region evacuates children after deadly clashes | publisher = Channel NewsAsis | date = 2008-08-05 | url = http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_world/view/364929/1/.html | accessdate = 2008-08-10 | archive-date = 2008-09-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080911190453/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/afp_world/view/364929/1/.html | dead-url = no }}</ref> 自从俄罗斯自2006年6月封锁了[[卡兹别吉|卡兹别吉]]-[[Verkhni_Lars|Verkhni Lars]]海关检查站后，罗克斯基隧道成为了连接南奥塞梯和俄罗斯的唯一通道。<ref>{{cite news | last = Evans | first = Michael | title = Georgia: Reckless Saakashvili took on Russian Goliath Putin | publisher = ''[[Times_Online|Times Online]]'' | date = 2008-08-11 | url = http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/europe/article4500160.ece | accessdate = 2008-08-11 | archive-date = 2008-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080903224407/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/europe/article4500160.ece | dead-url = no }}</ref>

